  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bc2\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bbf \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Recovery of pain reliever pills that were to be smuggled from Tuticorin to Sri Lanka",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Tamil Nadu Q Division police have seized the pain relief pills that were being smuggled from Tamil Nadu to Sri Lanka.",
        "The Q Division police received information that pain relief pills were being smuggled to Sri Lanka from Threspuram beach in Thoothukudi district.",
        "After this, the Q Division police searched a suspiciously parked country boat without a registration number on the Threspuram beach.",
        "Out of which 4430 pain relief pills were recovered in about 443 cards for smuggling to Sri Lanka.",
        "Q Division police handed over the recovered painkillers and the country boat to the customs officials."
      ],
